{"event_type": "planner.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"event_type": "codex.raw.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_26", "text": "I\u2019ve confirmed the final stage is currently focused on export controls and rewrite review, while the richer read/listen experience already exists elsewhere in the audio stage. I\u2019m now tracing which snapshot fields already expose story text and streamable audio so I can pull those into finalize without duplicating backend work unnecessarily.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T19:50:06.727971-07:00"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "text": "I\u2019ve confirmed the final stage is currently focused on export controls and rewrite review, while the richer read/listen experience already exists elsewhere in the audio stage. I\u2019m now tracing which snapshot fields already expose story text and streamable audio so I can pull those into finalize without duplicating backend work unnecessarily.", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T19:50:06.727971-07:00"}
