{"event_type": "planner.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"event_type": "codex.raw.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_63", "text": "I\u2019m at the edit point now. The plan is to keep backend contracts untouched, add one frontend helper for loading text assets, reshape `FinalizeStage` into a tabbed read/listen experience with clear fallback states, and add CSS/tests around that rather than spreading logic into the workspace page.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T19:53:22.840830-07:00"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "text": "I\u2019m at the edit point now. The plan is to keep backend contracts untouched, add one frontend helper for loading text assets, reshape `FinalizeStage` into a tabbed read/listen experience with clear fallback states, and add CSS/tests around that rather than spreading logic into the workspace page.", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T19:53:22.840830-07:00"}
