{"event_type": "planner.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"event_type": "codex.raw.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_148", "text": "The Docker engine still won\u2019t come up, so I\u2019m not going to wait indefinitely on a blocked daemon. I\u2019m switching to a browser fallback: run the frontend locally, mock the session API responses in the browser, and capture finalize-stage screenshots that way so visual verification still happens in this batch run.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T20:07:52.008652-07:00"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "text": "The Docker engine still won\u2019t come up, so I\u2019m not going to wait indefinitely on a blocked daemon. I\u2019m switching to a browser fallback: run the frontend locally, mock the session API responses in the browser, and capture finalize-stage screenshots that way so visual verification still happens in this batch run.", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T20:07:52.008652-07:00"}
