{"event_type": "planner.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"event_type": "codex.raw.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_163", "text": "The first fallback script failed because the Playwright package isn\u2019t installed in the repo, only available through `npx`. I\u2019m rerunning the browser capture using an ephemeral `npx -p playwright` invocation so I can still mock the API and take screenshots without adding dependencies.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T20:10:10.102289-07:00"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "text": "The first fallback script failed because the Playwright package isn\u2019t installed in the repo, only available through `npx`. I\u2019m rerunning the browser capture using an ephemeral `npx -p playwright` invocation so I can still mock the API and take screenshots without adding dependencies.", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T20:10:10.102289-07:00"}
